info.title: EDE API
info.description: Zipari API wrapper for integration with CMS EDE APIs

get.description: Use either Application ID or PTN query parameters to look up a summary view of applications. If requested via Application ID, all application versions (including deleted versions) return in the response from the FFE to the Requester via the Hub if the Application ID exists. If requested via PTN, a summary of all applications with which the PTN is associated with returns in the response from the FFE to the Requester via the Hub.
